---
// No hay importaciones necesarias por ahora
---

<!-- Experience Section -->
<div class="space-y-6 lg:space-y-8 w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 lg:px-0">
  
  <!-- Sticky Title for Mobile -->
  <div class="lg:hidden sticky top-16 z-40 bg-dark/80 backdrop-blur-sm py-4 -mx-4 px-4 mb-6">
    <h2 class="text-light text-xl font-semibold tracking-wider">EXPERIENCIA</h2>
  </div>

  <!-- Experience Content -->
  <div class="space-y-6 lg:space-y-8 pt-[40px]">
    
    <!-- Experience Item 1 -->
    <div class="experience-item space-y-3 lg:space-y-0 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-8 cursor-pointer transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-primary/5 hover:border-primary/20 rounded-lg p-4 border border-transparent">
      <!-- Date Column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-3">
        <div class="text-muted text-sm lg:text-xs font-medium lg:sticky lg:top-24">
          2025 - PRESENTE
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Content Column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-9 space-y-3 lg:space-y-4">
        <!-- Company/Project Title -->
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
          <h3 class="text-light text-lg lg:text-xl font-semibold">CooWeb LLC</h3>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 lg:w-5 lg:h-5 text-muted" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Description -->
        <p class="text-muted text-lg lg:text-base leading-relaxed text-left">
          Donec nec dolor tortor. Pellentesque nibh lacus, laoreet et finibus non, convallis ut enim. Nunc dapibus ornare erat id malesuada. Donec tincidunt cursus purus. Quisque elementum blandit elementum.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Technologies -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="tech-tag px-3 py-1 lg:px-4 lg:py-2 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm lg:text-sm rounded-full border border-primary/20">
            JavaScript
          </span>
          <span class="tech-tag px-3 py-1 lg:px-4 lg:py-2 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm lg:text-sm rounded-full border border-primary/20">
            TypeScript
          </span>
          <span class="tech-tag px-3 py-1 lg:px-4 lg:py-2 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm lg:text-sm rounded-full border border-primary/20">
            Astro
          </span>
          <span class="tech-tag px-3 py-1 lg:px-4 lg:py-2 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm lg:text-sm rounded-full border border-primary/20">
            Bootstrap
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Experience Item 2 -->
    <div class="experience-item space-y-3 lg:space-y-0 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-8 cursor-pointer transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-primary/5 hover:border-primary/20 rounded-lg p-4 border border-transparent">
      <!-- Date Column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-3">
        <div class="text-muted text-sm lg:text-xs font-medium lg:sticky lg:top-24">
          2024 - PRESENTE
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Content Column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-9 space-y-3 lg:space-y-4">
        <!-- Company/Project Title -->
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
          <h3 class="text-light text-lg lg:text-xl font-semibold">Freelance Developer</h3>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 lg:w-5 lg:h-5 text-muted" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Description -->
        <p class="text-muted text-lg lg:text-base leading-relaxed text-left">
          Desarrollo de aplicaciones web personalizadas y sitios corporativos para diversos clientes. Implementación de soluciones escalables utilizando tecnologías modernas y mejores prácticas de desarrollo.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Technologies -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="tech-tag px-3 py-1 lg:px-4 lg:py-2 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm lg:text-sm rounded-full border border-primary/20">
            React
          </span>
          <span class="tech-tag px-3 py-1 lg:px-4 lg:py-2 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm lg:text-sm rounded-full border border-primary/20">
            Node.js
          </span>
          <span class="tech-tag px-3 py-1 lg:px-4 lg:py-2 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm lg:text-sm rounded-full border border-primary/20">
            MongoDB
          </span>
          <span class="tech-tag px-3 py-1 lg:px-4 lg:py-2 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm lg:text-sm rounded-full border border-primary/20">
            Tailwind CSS
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Experience Item 3 -->
    <div class="experience-item space-y-3 lg:space-y-0 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-8 cursor-pointer transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-primary/5 hover:border-primary/20 rounded-lg p-4 border border-transparent">
      <!-- Date Column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-3">
        <div class="text-muted text-sm lg:text-xs font-medium lg:sticky lg:top-24">
          2023 - 2024
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Content Column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-9 space-y-3 lg:space-y-4">
        <!-- Company/Project Title -->
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
          <h3 class="text-light text-lg lg:text-xl font-semibold">Proyectos Académicos</h3>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 lg:w-5 lg:h-5 text-muted" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Description -->
        <p class="text-muted text-lg lg:text-base leading-relaxed text-left">
          Desarrollo de múltiples proyectos durante mi formación como ingeniero de sistemas. Creación de aplicaciones web, APIs RESTful y bases de datos para resolver problemas reales del sector educativo y empresarial.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Technologies -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="tech-tag px-3 py-1 lg:px-4 lg:py-2 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm lg:text-sm rounded-full border border-primary/20">
            Python
          </span>
          <span class="tech-tag px-3 py-1 lg:px-4 lg:py-2 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm lg:text-sm rounded-full border border-primary/20">
            Django
          </span>
          <span class="tech-tag px-3 py-1 lg:px-4 lg:py-2 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm lg:text-sm rounded-full border border-primary/20">
            PostgreSQL
          </span>
          <span class="tech-tag px-3 py-1 lg:px-4 lg:py-2 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm lg:text-sm rounded-full border border-primary/20">
            Vue.js
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

</div>

<style>
  .tech-tag {
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .tech-tag:hover {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-dark);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.3);
  }

  .experience-item {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .experience-item:not(:last-child)::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0%, var(--color-primary)/20 50%, transparent 100%);
  }

  /* Desktop optimizations */
  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .experience-item {
      padding-bottom: 2rem;
    }
  }

  /* Mobile optimizations */
  @media (max-width: 1023px) {
    .experience-item {
      padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style> 